datasets.name: 3adff942
datasets.query:
Select
  results.workspaceid as workspaceid,
  concat(
    results.category,
    ' (Out of ',
    category_count,
    ')'
  ) as category,
  severity,
  severity_count,
  ord
FROM
  (
    SELECT
      sbp.category,
      sbp.severity,
      sc.workspaceid,
      count(sbp.severity) severity_count,
      CASE
        WHEN sbp.severity = 'High' THEN 3
        WHEN sbp.severity = 'Medium' THEN 2
        ELSE 1
      END as ord
    FROM
      main.security_analysis.security_checks sc,
      main.security_analysis.security_best_practices sbp
    where
      score = 1
      and sc.id = sbp.id
      and run_id = coalesce (
        (
          select
            max(run_id)
          from
            main.security_analysis.workspace_run_complete
          where
            completed = true
        ),
        (
          select
            max(run_id)
          from
            main.security_analysis.workspace_run_complete
          where
            completed = true
        )
      )
      and category not IN ('Workspace Settings', 'Workspace Stats')
    group by
    sc.workspaceid,
      sbp.category,
      sbp.severity
  ) as results,
  (
    SELECT
      category,
      count(*) as category_count
    FROM
      main.security_analysis.security_best_practices
    WHERE
      category not IN ('Workspace Settings', 'Workspace Stats')
    group by
      category
  ) as master
where
  results.category = master.category

datasets.name: f2d75b91
datasets.query:
select
  sbp.check_id,
  sbp.check,
  sbp.recommendation,
  sc.additional_details,
  sbp.logic,
  if(
    sbp.evaluation_value == "-1",
    "N/A",
    sbp.evaluation_value
  ) as evaluation_value,
  regexp_replace(sbp.api, "<workspace_url>", aw.deployment_url) as api,
  sc.check_time
from
  main.security_analysis.security_checks sc,
  main.security_analysis.security_best_practices sbp,
  main.security_analysis.account_workspaces aw
where
  sc.id = sbp.id
  and sc.run_id = coalesce (
    (
      select
        max(run_id)
      from
        main.security_analysis.workspace_run_complete
      where
        completed = true
    ),
    (
      select
        max(run_id)
      from
        main.security_analysis.workspace_run_complete
      where
        completed = true
    )
  )
  and aw.workspace_id = sc.workspaceid
